    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着关税焦虑偏移的静音CPI，美国的信用恐惧增加了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/credit-fear-gauges-worsen-as-tariff-concerns-offset-soft-cpi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当投资者担心关税的经济影响时，对公司信贷违约的担忧升级，尽管美国通货膨胀数据在新征税之前对消费者有所缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/credit-fear-gauges-worsen-as-tariff-concerns-offset-soft-cpi</guid>
